  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5472891">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5472891/" class="title-link">差强人意</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5472891"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/azhuai/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1107126-8.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/azhuai/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">周公度</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-06-20"
      class="main-meta">2012-06-20 11:53:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5472891_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  多数辞条“启蒙”的意义已经过去。近于老生常谈。 虽然如此，但伏尔泰对宗教的态度和表达时的勇气依然令人惊讶。为什么在伏尔泰的时代对宗教的质疑如此彻底，已经纵谈“信仰自由”，今日中国却令众学者噤若寒蝉？ 另外，该书对圣经与基督教的质疑颇多，作为伏尔泰的理想寄托，...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
