  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3600208">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3600208/" class="title-link">哲学辞典，关于常识</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3600208"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/43212911/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u43212911-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/43212911/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Lee</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-27"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-27 15:08:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3600208_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  给我的感觉是以一种另类的观点阐述常识，在这个缺乏信仰的时代，常识亦是最容易被人们忽略的东西。人们在不断追求物质的过程中，与精神渐行渐远，许多常识只能被重新认识或者曲解。 

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            北京出版社2008版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3600208_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3600208_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





