            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="34454338">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">古代圣人阴茎供人亲吻,故导致割礼,乃卫生计也.
古人发誓需摸着阴囊,故法文证人愚阴囊同词根也.</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-03-03 21:45</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                古代圣人阴茎供人亲吻,故导致割礼,乃卫生计也.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>古人发誓需摸着阴囊,故法文证人愚阴囊同词根也.
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
