              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/13973816/" class="">第211页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/weifugu/" class=" " title="[已注销]">[已注销]</a>
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="13973816">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">to kalon~希腊语就是the beautiful的意思~~特此说明</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-08-02 21:17</span>
                  
                </p>
